latestPosts.caption:
My bride wanted a soft, natural look for her big day — and I loved bringing her vision to life! 💕
She asked for:
✔️ Naturally filled brows
✔️ Glowing, radiant skin
✔️ A soft glam with no lashes (she’s allergic to lash glue)

We kept it fresh, light, and timeless — just like her 🕊️
It’s always such a joy to create exactly what my brides envision for one of the most special days of their lives 💍💄
#BridalMakeup #SoftGlam #NaturalBride #WeddingMakeup #GlowingSkin #MakeupArtist #BridalBeauty #NoLashesNeeded
